Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.88,0:19:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,估计是你压根就没怀孕吧\N{\fnArial\fs38}Hmm, I guess you never were pregnant.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.82,0:20:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我应该是把Ethel的卵巢囊肿放你肚子里了\N{\fnArial\fs38}I must have transferred an ovarian cyst from Ethel's body into yours,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.38,0:20:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,当时以为是个胎儿呢\N{\fnArial\fs38}thinking it was an embryo.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.70,0:20:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,那么超声检查还有婚检\N{\fnArial\fs38}What about the ultrasound and the checkups
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.20,0:20:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,和天拉维的基因测试是怎么回事?\N{\fnArial\fs38}And the Skymall dna test?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.94,0:20:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,天拉维的产品全都是垃圾\N{\fnArial\fs38}Well, Skymall products are shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.98,0:20:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,其他检测结果不准确是因为我嗑药嗑晕了\N{\fnArial\fs38}The rest are oversights that result from having your own prescription pad.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.04,0:20:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我要走了\N{\fnArial\fs38}Well, I'm out of here,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.20,0:20:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,看我用天拉维的飞鼠服飞出去\N{\fnArial\fs38}Using my patented Skymall flying squirrel suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.60,0:20:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,天拉维\N{\fnArial\fs38}Skymall!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.28,0:20:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 我走了\N{\fnArial\fs38}All right. I'm leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.54,0:20:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,别急 这货要是个肿瘤 选择权在谁手里?\N{\fnArial\fs38}Wait. So if it was a tumor, whose choice was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.18,0:20:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你不知道 你不知道\N{\fnArial\fs38}You don't know. You don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.32,0:20:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你不知道\N{\fnArial\fs38}You don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.82,0:20:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,说实话 我们都不知道\N{\fnArial\fs38}And none of us do, frankly.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.38,0:20:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,堕胎是非常复杂的问题\N{\fnArial\fs38}Abortion is a very complicated issue.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.62,0:20:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,谁特么在乎啊 我们不是要去猫头鹰餐厅的嘛\N{\fnArial\fs38}Oh, who gives a shit? I thought we were going to Hooters.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.32,0:20:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,看来皆大欢喜了\N{\fnArial\fs38}Well, all's well that ends well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.96,0:20:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我把这拿去当肉馅了 - 不要\N{\fnArial\fs38}- I'll go grind this into taco meat. - No!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.64,0:20:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我要留下它\N{\fnArial\fs38}I'm keeping it!
